items.title: Dave & Buster’s Tempe will debut Sunday Funday
items.summary:
Starting on Sunday, September 24, and every Sunday after, Dave and Buster’s at Tempe Marketplace is debuting Sunday Funday from 12 p.m. to 4 p.m. on the roof top patio! Play games like ping pong, giant jenga, corn hole and cup pong while listening to the live DJ. Enjoy delicious $5 select appetizers or the create your own bloody mary and mimosa bar! items.title: Famous Dave’s celebrates founder’s BBQ Hall of Fame induction
items.summary:
Famous Dave’s of America, Inc. recently announced the company’s founder, “Famous Dave” Anderson was named to the 2017 Barbecue Hall of Fame by the American Royal Association. American Royal held the formal induction ceremony at Kansas Speedway over Labor Day weekend. Each year, three individuals are awarded the prestigious honor and are recognized by the Barbecue Hall of Fame for their significant contributions to the barbecue community and demonstration of achievement in barbecue excellence.
